# start Validation Reply Form
_vrf_PLAT241_3_h_naphthalene_butyl_pbi4 
;
PROBLEM: High   'MainMol' Ueq as Compared to Neighbors of        C25 Check
RESPONSE: Room temperature data leads to uncertainty in exact centroid positions. This can be further parameterized and restrained but this masks innate diffuse disorder of atom position. 
;
_vrf_PLAT342_3_h_naphthalene_butyl_pbi4 
;
PROBLEM: Low Bond Precision on  C-C Bonds ...............    0.05929 Ang.
RESPONSE: Result of room temperature measurement and poor resolution of sample. This precision does not hinder the interpretation of results for this work. 
;
_vrf_PLAT987_3_h_naphthalene_butyl_pbi4 
